org.locationtech.geowave.core.store.data

Class SingleFieldPersistentDataset<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.locationtech.geowave.core.store.data.SingleFieldPersistentDataset<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The most specific generalization for the type for all of the values in this dataset.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    PersistentDataset<T>

    public class SingleFieldPersistentDataset<T>
extends Object
implements PersistentDataset<T>
    This is a basic mapping of field ID to native field type. "Native" in this sense can be to either the data adapter or the common index, depending on whether it is in the common index or is an extended field.
